{
  "video_id": "CdbBwIgq4rs",
  "title": "The science of smog - Kim Preshoff",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7966.0,
      "end_time": 10982.0,
      "text": "On July 26, 1943,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10982.0,
      "end_time": 14567.0,
      "text": "Los Angeles was blanketed by a thick gas that stung people's eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14567.0,
      "end_time": 16582.0,
      "text": "and blocked out the Sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16582.0,
      "end_time": 21451.0,
      "text": "Panicked residents believed their city had been attacked using chemical warfare."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21451.0,
      "end_time": 23912.0,
      "text": "But the cloud wasn't an act of war."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23912.0,
      "end_time": 25599.0,
      "text": "It was smog."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25599.0,
      "end_time": 28790.0,
      "text": "A portmanteau of smoke and fog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28790.0,
      "end_time": 31957.0,
      "text": "the word smog was coined at the beginning of the 20th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31957.0,
      "end_time": 34678.0,
      "text": "to describe the thick gray haze that covered cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34678.0,
      "end_time": 35684.0,
      "text": "such as London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35684.0,
      "end_time": 36393.0,
      "text": "Glasgow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36393.0,
      "end_time": 38768.0,
      "text": "and Edinburgh."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38768.0,
      "end_time": 40888.0,
      "text": "This industrial smog was known to form"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40888.0,
      "end_time": 44358.0,
      "text": "when smoke from coal-burning home stoves and factories"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44359.0,
      "end_time": 47118.0,
      "text": "combined with moisture in the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47118.0,
      "end_time": 50288.0,
      "text": "But the smog behind the LA panic was different."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50288.0,
      "end_time": 53540.0,
      "text": "It was yellowish with a chemical odor."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53540.0,
      "end_time": 57319.0,
      "text": "Since the city didn't burn much coal, its cause would remain a mystery"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57319.0,
      "end_time": 62258.0,
      "text": "until a chemist named Arie Haagen-Smit identified two culprits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62258.0,
      "end_time": 65758.0,
      "text": "volatile organic compounds, or VOCs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65758.0,
      "end_time": 68701.0,
      "text": "and nitrogen oxides."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68701.0,
      "end_time": 71509.0,
      "text": "VOCs are compounds that easily become vapors"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71510.0,
      "end_time": 73709.0,
      "text": "and may contain elements, such as carbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73709.0,
      "end_time": 74740.0,
      "text": "oxygen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74740.0,
      "end_time": 75740.0,
      "text": "hydrogen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75740.0,
      "end_time": 76651.0,
      "text": "chlorine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76651.0,
      "end_time": 78298.0,
      "text": "and sulfur."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78299.0,
      "end_time": 80989.0,
      "text": "Some are naturally produced by plants and animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80989.0,
      "end_time": 83120.0,
      "text": "but others come from manmade sources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83120.0,
      "end_time": 84130.0,
      "text": "like solvents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84130.0,
      "end_time": 85181.0,
      "text": "paints,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85181.0,
      "end_time": 85979.0,
      "text": "glues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85979.0,
      "end_time": 87681.0,
      "text": "and petroleum."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87681.0,
      "end_time": 91420.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the incomplete combustion of gas in motor vehicles"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91421.0,
      "end_time": 94410.0,
      "text": "releases nitrogen oxides."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 94410.0,
      "end_time": 98390.0,
      "text": "That's what gives this type of smog its yellowish color."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98400.0,
      "end_time": 101722.0,
      "text": "VOCs and nitrogen oxide react with sunlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101722.0,
      "end_time": 106211.0,
      "text": "to produce secondary pollutants called PANs and tropospheric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106212.0,
      "end_time": 109131.0,
      "text": "or ground level, ozone."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109131.0,
      "end_time": 113922.0,
      "text": "PANs and ozone cause eye irritation and damage lung tissue."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113922.0,
      "end_time": 117210.0,
      "text": "Both are key ingredients in photochemical smog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 117220.0,
      "end_time": 120730.0,
      "text": "which is what had been plaguing LA."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 120730.0,
      "end_time": 123661.0,
      "text": "So why does smog affect some cities but not others?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123662.0,
      "end_time": 128332.0,
      "text": "Both industrial and photochemical smog combine manmade pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128332.0,
      "end_time": 130983.0,
      "text": "with local weather and geography."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130983.0,
      "end_time": 135933.0,
      "text": "London's high humidity made it a prime location for industrial smog."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 135933.0,
      "end_time": 139634.0,
      "text": "Photochemical smog is strongest in urban areas with calm winds"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139634.0,
      "end_time": 142384.0,
      "text": "and dry, warm, sunny weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142384.0,
      "end_time": 145933.0,
      "text": "The ultraviolet radiation from sunlight provides the energy necessary"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145933.0,
      "end_time": 150840.0,
      "text": "to breakdown molecules that contribute to smog formation."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150840.0,
      "end_time": 152743.0,
      "text": "Cities surrounded by mountains, like LA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152743.0,
      "end_time": 155430.0,
      "text": "or lying in a basin, like Beijing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155430.0,
      "end_time": 160613.0,
      "text": "are also especially vulnerable to smog since there's nowhere for it to dissipate."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160613.0,
      "end_time": 164814.0,
      "text": "That's also partially due to a phenomenon known as temperature inversion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164814.0,
      "end_time": 167894.0,
      "text": "where instead of warm air continuously rising upward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167894.0,
      "end_time": 172135.0,
      "text": "a pollution-filled layer of air remains trapped near the Earth's surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 172135.0,
      "end_time": 175143.0,
      "text": "by a slightly warmer layer above."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 175144.0,
      "end_time": 178340.0,
      "text": "Smog isn't just an aesthetic eyesore."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178340.0,
      "end_time": 180185.0,
      "text": "Both forms of smog irritate the eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180186.0,
      "end_time": 180955.0,
      "text": "nose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180955.0,
      "end_time": 181825.0,
      "text": "and throat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181825.0,
      "end_time": 184726.0,
      "text": "exacerbate conditions like asthma and emphysema,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184727.0,
      "end_time": 189296.0,
      "text": "and increase the risk of respiratory infections like bronchitis."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189296.0,
      "end_time": 192845.0,
      "text": "Smog can be especially harmful to young children and older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 192845.0,
      "end_time": 196640.0,
      "text": "and exposure in pregnant women has been linked to low birth weight"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196640.0,
      "end_time": 198505.0,
      "text": "and potential birth defects."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 198505.0,
      "end_time": 201356.0,
      "text": "Secondary pollutants found in photochemical smog"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201356.0,
      "end_time": 204755.0,
      "text": "can damage and weaken crops and decrease yield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204755.0,
      "end_time": 207825.0,
      "text": "making them more susceptible to insects."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207825.0,
      "end_time": 212487.0,
      "text": "Yet for decades, smog was seen as the inevitable price of civilization."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212487.0,
      "end_time": 216626.0,
      "text": "Londoners had become accustomed to the notorious pea soup fog"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216627.0,
      "end_time": 219727.0,
      "text": "swirling over their streets until 1952,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 219727.0,
      "end_time": 224575.0,
      "text": "when the Great Smog of London shut down all transportation in the city for days"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 224575.0,
      "end_time": 228929.0,
      "text": "and caused more  than 4,000 respiratory deaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 228929.0,
      "end_time": 232387.0,
      "text": "As a result, the Clean Air Act of 1956"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 232387.0,
      "end_time": 235586.0,
      "text": "banned burning coal in certain areas of the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 235586.0,
      "end_time": 238554.0,
      "text": "leading to a massive reduction in smog."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 238554.0,
      "end_time": 242847.0,
      "text": "Similarly, regulations on vehicle emissions and gas content in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242847.0,
      "end_time": 247838.0,
      "text": "reduced the volatile compounds in the air and smog levels along with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247838.0,
      "end_time": 251537.0,
      "text": "Smog remains a major problem around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 251538.0,
      "end_time": 254968.0,
      "text": "Countries like China and Poland that depend on coal for energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254968.0,
      "end_time": 258178.0,
      "text": "experience high levels of industrial smog."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258178.0,
      "end_time": 261617.0,
      "text": "Photochemical smog and airborne particles from vehicle emissions"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261617.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263989.0,
      "text": "affect many rapidly developing cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263989.0,
      "end_time": 266359.0,
      "text": "from Mexico City and Santiago"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266359.0,
      "end_time": 269339.0,
      "text": "to New Delhi and Tehran."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 269339.0,
      "end_time": 271658.0,
      "text": "Governments have tried many methods to tackle it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 271658.0,
      "end_time": 276784.0,
      "text": "such as banning cars from driving for days at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276784.0,
      "end_time": 280159.0,
      "text": "As more than half of the world's population crowds into cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 280159.0,
      "end_time": 284110.0,
      "text": "considering a shift to mass transit and away from fossil fuels"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 284110.0,
      "end_time": 285990.0,
      "text": "may allow us to breathe easier."
    }
  ]
}